Xulfi Bhai has set new standards for Coke Studio 14 and 15!

And Momina’s voice has touched our souls!

But I came here to thank and appreciate Adnan Dhool for writing such wonderful lyrics for this song and "Tu Jhoom."

The lyrics are mesmerizing and beautiful. It is surely a masterpiece!

Thank you, Adnan Sir 🙏. You are a living legend 🤩.
